## Unpaid Amounts ##

Amounts owing from to a non-arms lenth person to a taxpayer cannot be deducted if the amount is not paid bythe end fo the taxpayer's second taxation year following the year in which it was incurred.[^unpaid-non-arms-length]

## Footnotes ##

[^unpaid-non-arms-length]: ITA ss. 78(1)
